WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.312 --> 00:00:02.285
It is important for any organization

2
00:00:02.285 --> 00:00:05.909
to have well written policies and other reference guides,

3
00:00:05.909 --> 00:00:08.992
which allow management to guide operations efficiently

4
00:00:08.992 --> 00:00:10.552
and accurately.

5
00:00:10.552 --> 00:00:13.136
These policy and reference guides allow departments

6
00:00:13.136 --> 00:00:15.867
and employees to clearly understand their roles

7
00:00:15.867 --> 00:00:17.688
and responsibilities.

8
00:00:17.688 --> 00:00:20.666
The government has many laws, policies and regulations

9
00:00:20.666 --> 00:00:23.141
that determine how staff should perform duties

10
00:00:23.141 --> 00:00:25.731
in the best interest of patient care.

11
00:00:25.731 --> 00:00:28.856
These are all arranged in a policy hierarchy.

12
00:00:28.856 --> 00:00:31.821
A policy hierarchy within a government organization

13
00:00:31.821 --> 00:00:34.572
is when laws, policies and regulations are given

14
00:00:34.572 --> 00:00:36.875
and followed in a certain order.

15
00:00:36.875 --> 00:00:39.757
Next we will discuss the policies and reference guides

16
00:00:39.757 --> 00:00:41.339
in place for your use.

